for freeing humanity

00:15:31.350 --> 00:15:34.260
from oligarchs and
tyrants dressed up as a

00:15:34.260 --> 00:15:37.500
get rich quick scheme.

00:15:37.500 --> 00:15:39.470
So I guess the last
thought to leave you with

00:15:39.470 --> 00:15:42.870
is that Bitcoin has implications
not just for finance

00:15:42.870 --> 00:15:47.040
and commerce, but for
politics, digital privacy, law

00:15:47.040 --> 00:15:49.800
enforcement, even citizenship.

00:15:49.800 --> 00:15:51.570
Its story opens a
window onto some

00:15:51.570 --> 00:15:53.820
of the most important
issues of our time.

