become harder with time

00:18:03.180 --> 00:18:05.479
in order to keep
up with Moore's law

00:18:05.479 --> 00:18:07.770
because obviously computers
are a lot more powerful now

00:18:07.770 --> 00:18:09.540
than they were in 2009.

00:18:09.540 --> 00:18:12.270
